Description:
Spread Your Wings
The comfortable living and entertaining space both inside and out, underlines the intelligent concepts that have been beautifully expressed by this 4 bedroom stunner.
Set in arguably Derrimut's most sought after pocket with shops, schools, parks, recreational facilities, new golf course and transport nearby.
This 32 sq family residence include; Relaxing master bedroom, having a full en-suite with double vanity, double sized shower, spa bath, WIR, over sized bedrooms with built in computer desks, formal lounge, study nook, well equipped kitchen with lots of cupboards, open plan living, family/meals areas, rumpus/games room and bright 3 way central bathroom with access to two bedrooms.
Extras; French doors, quality windows, ducted heating, refrigerated cooling,
900 mm s/s appliances, dishwasher provision, walk in pantry, walk in linen, 6x7m pergola, 6x3m garden shed, 6000 litre water tank connected to toilets, solar hot water, low maintenance gardens, drive thru double remote garage on a wonderful allotment measuring 777 sum.
The scope and potential makes this a unique opportunity one must inspect.
Simon Baresic : 0416 101 307

Beautifully presented and ideally situated is this 4 bedroom family home that will cater for all your needs. With it's delightful open plan living and modern features, you will never want to leave home again.
Comprising:- 4 bedrooms, BIR's, main with en suite & WIR, open living room, well equipped kitchen ,
meals / family areas, peaceful entertaining alfresco & pergola and double garage.
Features: Central heating-cooling, stainless/steel appliances & s dishwasher, remote controlled garage door, solar hot water unit & landscaped gardens on a 550sqm allotment.
Bonuses:- Close to Sunshine Golf Club, schools, transport and shopping with easy access to Ballarat & Western Ring Roads.
Simon Baresic : 0416 101 307

Description:
FAMILY FAVORITE
With great space and presented as new, this four bedroom home will certainly impress and
offer itself to the market in pristine condition.
Featuring four bedrooms, master with walk in robe and ensuite, with the three other bedrooms being accompanied by built in robes and serviced by a second bathroom.
The squeaky clean kitchen features stainless steel gas cook top and dishwasher and overlooks the meals area and main living space.
Set on an ultra low maintenance block, this home would be ideal to move into or maintain as an investment with a great tenant.
Please contact Pennisi Real Estate on 9379-5616 for your personal inspection.

Description:
Ticks All The Right Boxes
Take pride in owning this modern well designed home, perfectly positioned overlooking the park, close to the school, child care, recreation reserve and public transport. With great access to Ballarat Road, Western Highway and newly developed Sunshine golf course.
Comprising: 4 bedrooms, en-suite and walk in robe, BIR's, formal lounge, open plan kitchen, dining & family areas opening to pergola-entertaining area, good sized backyard and
double garage.
Features: 2 street frontages, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, s/s appliances-dishwasher, remote controlled garage door, water tank connected to toilets.
